---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base
  title="cv-onepager (built by DevSwarm) — Tom Scholtes"
  description="Single-file CV one-pager produced end-to-end by the DevSwarm five-persona pipeline in 4m 42s."
  path="/projects/devswarm-cv"
>
  <Nav active="projects" />
  <main>
    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <article class="prose">
          <div class="meta">Demo · DevSwarm output</div>
          <h1>cv-onepager — the swarm built this.</h1>
          <p style="font-size:20px; color:var(--ink)">
            Look ma: a static CV one-pager produced end-to-end by the five-persona DevSwarm
            pipeline. Single HTML file, inline CSS, accessible motion, no JavaScript, no CDN.
          </p>

          <h2>Run summary</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Idea</strong> — "Build a CV one-pager that fades in."</li>
            <li><strong>Architect</strong> — Produced PLAN.md with acceptance greps for h1, fade-in keyframes, dark background, no script tags, no external resources.</li>
            <li><strong>Researcher</strong> — Produced RESEARCH.md with the flexbox centering + <code>@keyframes fadeIn</code> + <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code> patterns.</li>
            <li><strong>Frontend</strong> — Wrote the single <code>index.html</code> file, ran the eight acceptance greps locally, all pass.</li>
            <li><strong>Backend</strong> — No-op (spec is static frontend only).</li>
            <li><strong>Reviewer-Deployer</strong> — Verified greps, packaged the artifact, opened the PR.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Wall-clock</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>4m 42s</strong> from prompt to opened PR. Cv-onepager run timestamp:
            <code>2026-05-12 19:46:03</code>.
          </p>

          <h2>Embedded artifact</h2>
          <p>
            (Below is a placeholder for the cv-onepager iframe; once the artifact is hosted, the
            Reviewer-Deployer wires the iframe src to the PR's GitHub Pages preview URL.)
          </p>
          <pre><code>&lt;iframe src="/og/cv-onepager.html" style="width:100%; height:600px; border:1px solid var(--rule); border-radius:14px"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</code></pre>

          <p style="margin-top:48px"><a href="/projects">← Back to projects</a></p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
